name: Pedro Pascal
description:
José Pedro Balmaceda Pascal; born 2 April 1975, is a Chilean-born American actor. After nearly two decades of taking small roles in film and television, Pascal rose to prominence for portraying Oberyn Martell during the fourth season of the HBO fantasy series Game of Thrones (2014) and Javier Peña in the Netflix crime series Narcos (2015–2017). Since 2019, he has starred in the series The Mandalorian and again in The Book of Boba Fett (2022). Since 2023, he has played Joel in The Last of Us.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Here's a textual inversion of Pedro Pascal. I used 30 public images of him. 3000 steps training. To use it in your works,

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • Then simply add pppascal to your prompt and enjoy!

  • Keep the Samples around 30, CFG between 7.5 and 8, but feel free to experiment as usual;

Have fun!
